root.message: The STAT_CONC_DEF field for indicator 3-1-2, translated into en
root.data:
Percentage of births assisted by skilled health workers is the number of women giving birth in the reporting period who were assisted by skilled health workers per 100 women giving birth in the same period.

Skilled medical staff including obstetricians from orientation and above, midwives and above, obstetricians and paediatricians, and other certified medical staff who have been trained in procedures on “skilled birth attendants” under the program of the Ministry of Health.
